1
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:22,289
Mr. Lu, are we heading back to the company now?

2
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,860
Let's get in the car first.

3
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:27,200
But you have a meeting this morning.

4
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,080
Cancel it.

5
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:10,360
Lu Jingheng is the first

6
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,800
and the only person

7
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:14,720
I feel I can rely on.

8
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,730
How are you driving?

9
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,930
Mr. Lu, we have a situation.

10
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,079
What situation?

11
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,079
What do you mean?

12
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,600
A new script?

13
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,760
I already said no.

14
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,720
You.

15
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,240
Good morning.

16
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,400
Mr. Shen, you rushed back to the country.

17
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:08,400
I really thought you were worried about your daughter.

18
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,320
I didn't expect

19
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:12,160
you came to speak for an outsider like Su Yuran.

20
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,080
Lu Jingheng is one of our own,

21
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,280
but this kid always sides with outsiders,

22
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,480
unwilling to help me.

23
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:22,079
Fortunately, there are still sensible people in the Lu family.

24
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:23,540
A letter of understanding

25
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,800
gave your dad a way out.

26
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,640
Our family doesn't lose out.

27
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,440
Doesn't lose?

28
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,520
She almost killed me.

29
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:32,250
Why do you think I would sign something like this?

30
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,880
On what grounds?

31
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,600
Because you are my child.

32
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,760
No one knows you better than I do.

33
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:52,880
It's simple.

34
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:55,360
If you sign that letter of forgiveness,

35
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,079
that piece of paper will rot in my hands.

36
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,920
Of course, you don't have to sign it.

37
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:00,680
If you don't,

38
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,920
in court,

39
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:05,480
it might be more effective than the letter of forgiveness.

40
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,280
What makes you think a single photo

41
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,680
will convince everyone?

42
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:11,880
A single photo is indeed not enough proof.

43
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:15,080
But your mother is ironclad proof.

44
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,519
Have you forgotten how

45
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:17,959
crazy she was back then,

46
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,760
and how ugly her end was?

47
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,880
Genetics

48
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,160
can't be faked.

49
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:30,120
I am asking you to think it through right now.

50
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,320
I don't want to force you.

51
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:35,040
I don't want things to end up so ugly either.

52
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,020
It's just not worth it.

53
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,080
Are you sure you saw Shen Jingyao?

54
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:43,880
I'm positive.

55
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,540
Shen Jingyao was here.

56
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,330
What did he do to you?

57
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,020
What exactly did he do?

58
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:04,500
He wanted the accident settlement letter for Su Yuran.

59
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,920
I agreed.

60
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,850
Did he threaten you?

61
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,360
I'll go find him.

62
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,040
No need.

63
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,800
He didn't threaten me.

64
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,920
He just persuaded me.

65
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,120
If I give her a letter of forgiveness,

66
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,520
she still won't be completely exonerated.

67
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,050
After all, the DUI is a fact.

68
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:23,080
Even if it's not intentional injury,

69
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:24,800
she can't escape the dangerous driving charge.

70
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,530
The punishments she deserves,

71
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,690
she won't be able to escape any of them.

72
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,480
It's just that I still have to return to the Lu family

73
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,800
and see Su Manyun.

74
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,810
Making a big deal out of this

75
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,300
isn't good for anyone.

76
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,600
You don't need to worry about the Lu family.

77
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,330
Lu Jingheng.

78
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:41,040
I will handle my own affairs.

79
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:43,760
And...

80
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,800
I think I'm almost recovered.

81
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:48,770
I want to be discharged.

82
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:27,300
She always said she was tired,

83
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:29,000
and couldn't sleep well at night.

84
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,800
Her eyes would often flash with

85
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,860
an emptiness I couldn't understand.

86
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:34,920
If I had noticed it earlier,

87
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,200
would Mom still be here?

88
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:42,520
It's said that the original host's mother

89
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,800
died suddenly of an illness.

90
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:48,010
Then the original host's death...

91
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:52,240
One photo is indeed not enough proof.

92
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:55,440
But your mother is hard proof.

93
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:58,360
Have you forgotten how crazy she was,

94
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,220
and how terribly she passed away?

95
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,280
Genetics,

96
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,600
it can't be faked.

97
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,840
Your illness...

98
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:48,520
It keeps coming back.

99
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:49,680
It's been

100
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,840
many years.

101
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:54,720
Many years.

102
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,240
For every follow-up visit before,

103
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,920
didn't Mr. Shen accompany you?

104
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:06,840
Why did you come alone this time?

105
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,600
Doctor, you have no idea.

106
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,280
My dad has been so unlucky.

107
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,680
He broke his leg a while ago,

108
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,400
and it still hasn't fully healed.

109
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:15,520
I figured since I've had this illness

110
00:08:15,520 --> 00:08:16,720
for so many years,

111
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,280
it's fine to come by myself.

112
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:21,120
All right.

113
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:21,960
So tell me,

114
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:25,280
what's bothering you this time?

115
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,680
Lately,

116
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,240
my mental state has been very poor.

117
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,840
Mostly, I sleep very badly,

118
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,320
and I tend to have hallucinations.

119
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,360
Like what?

120
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,640
For instance, I keep seeing my mom.

121
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:43,400
Right before she passed away,

122
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,520
she used to stand at the door

123
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:46,280
like she had something to say,

124
00:08:46,520 --> 00:08:50,120
but she never actually said anything.

125
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:52,960
Doctor,

126
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:53,680
is my

127
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,560
paranoia getting worse again?

128
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:03,280
Don't overthink it.

129
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:05,320
You just haven't been resting well.

130
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:07,440
I'll prescribe you some sleep aids.

131
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:10,560
Take them and see if it helps.

132
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,960
I'm just scared.

133
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,280
You knew my mom, right?

134
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:15,520
Were her symptoms right before she died

135
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,880
very similar to mine?

136
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,440
Was she just like me before?

137
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:27,320
As for your mother's condition,

138
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,560
it's been too long.

139
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,080
I really can't remember.

140
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,520
Please don't say that, Doctor.

141
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:32,920
I know

142
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:34,880
this hospital must have her medical records.

143
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:36,040
Can't you try to recall it for me?

144
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,200
Let's focus on your matter today

145
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,200
and look at your condition first.

146
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,040
I'm just scared

147
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,440
that I might end up like my mom.

148
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:40,840
Today, I...

149
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,240
Doctor, please help me.

150
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:44,640
It's not that I don't want to check for you.

151
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:47,880
Your mother has already passed away.

152
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,080
According to hospital regulations,

153
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,520
this patient's file,

154
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:53,120
a deceased patient's file,

155
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:55,180
has long been sealed in the archives.

156
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:56,560
If you want to,

157
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,320
you can see it,

158
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:02,840
but you need Mr. Shen to apply for it with you.

159
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,080
Apply for it, right?

160
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,880
Yes.

161
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,800
Thank you.

162
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,520
Hello.

163
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,760
How do I get to the archives?

164
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:32,220
Go straight and turn left.

165
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,200
Thank you.

166
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:42,720
Hello.

167
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:43,720
Hello.

168
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:21,800
This way, Miss.

169
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,440
Shuyi.

170
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:34,140
The contract Uncle asked for.

171
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:37,600
I went out of my way to run errands for you.

172
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,780
Aren't you going to treat me to a meal?

173
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:42,280
Didn't you have a dinner appointment tonight?

174
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:44,600
You know my schedule so well.

175
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:49,960
The manager of Wenji Restaurant called to tell me

176
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:51,320
that you booked a private room

177
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,650
and specifically asked for a window seat.

178
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,130
Who are you meeting?

179
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,520
Is it Jingheng?

180
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,040
So what if it is?

181
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:02,800
Is it illegal for me to ask him out to dinner?

182
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:07,440
Shuyi, stop fooling around.

183
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:09,040
You're not a child anymore.

184
00:12:09,040 --> 00:12:11,900
It's time to take responsibility for your own life.

185
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:13,920
My life.

186
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:16,160
Since when is it your turn to manage it?

187
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,200
I'm your brother.

188
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,260
Jingheng is already married.

189
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,700
If you keep pestering him,

190
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:29,010
you'll only ruin yourself.

191
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:31,010
So what if I ruin myself?

192
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:34,280
I just fell in love with someone I shouldn't have.

193
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,080
What's wrong?

194
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,960
Don't I even have the right to like someone?

195
00:12:41,800 --> 00:12:43,040
Some feelings

196
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:47,400
should never have happened in the first place.

197
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,860
You don't understand my feelings at all.

198
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,320
You only know how to blindly stop me.

199
00:12:58,480 --> 00:12:59,600
I'm grown up.

200
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,200
You can't stop me.

201
00:13:03,880 --> 00:13:05,240
No one can.

